name: Approve
description: Approve the current agent output and advance the pipeline

---
The user has approved the current output.

1. Dispatch the Logger Agent to record this approval — write to the appropriate tasks/ file and update protocol/state.md session log
2. Increment the cycle counter in protocol/state.md if this completes a full pipeline cycle
3. Advance the pipeline state in protocol/state.md to the next stage

Then ask the user how they would like to proceed.
